<Class name="CM_WebUserAccessConfig" id="21c10e3c-3a4c-4bc5-a0ac-1b4743e35ec9">
    <superclass name="CM_Object"/>
    <persistentAllowed/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>This class is designed so we can hold associations between  
a cm_user  and any number of cm_operator, cm_carrier and
cm_consignorconsignees.

These associations are used by cms web applications as a 
page access profile for a user, and to define what tracked
items can be seen by a user.

There should eventually be methods on this class for exporting and importing 
this data.</text>
    <DbClassMap file="webclas"/>
    <Constant name="Carrier_Dict" id="bf6421b6-551b-4ab0-b3ed-f4da20b704cd">
        <source>"Carriers"</source>
        <type name="String"/>
    </Constant>
    <Constant name="Consign_Dict" id="58dda354-65ce-4cfe-be06-862fb928e8aa">
        <source>"Consignors"</source>
        <type name="String"/>
    </Constant>
    <Constant name="Dictionary_Error" id="eb79951c-0ca6-42b5-8e79-76a360ace89d">
        <source>2000</source>
        <type name="Integer"/>
    </Constant>
    <Constant name="Operator_Dict" id="787d3aa9-175a-4829-9397-964dbe11cfac">
        <source>"Operators"</source>
        <type name="String"/>
    </Constant>
